Description:
Framework opportunity for Residential Development Consultancy Services on behalf of Keystone Alliance.

Duration of Framework: 4 years.

Keystone Alliance is; Keystone Developments (LG) Ltd, Longhurst & Havelock Homes, Spire Homes, Axiom Housing Association, Friendship, Care and Housing, Lace Housing, Tuntum Housing Association and Framework Housing Association and could include any other Registered Provider, Local Authority or other Arms-Length Management Organisation situated in the English counties of Nottinghamshire, Lincolnshire, Leicestershire, Derbyshire, Northamptonshire, Rutland, Warwickshire (including the city of Birmingham), Bedfordshire, Norfolk, South Yorkshire, Staffordshire, Humberside, Cambridgeshire and Buckinghamshire].

The Alliance require Consultants to perform the services and roles of:
A. Employer's Agent (including optional Principal Designer services);
B. Architect (including optional Principal Designer services);
C. Clerk of Works;
D. Affordable Housing Project Manager.
